{"tid":962130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「東方日報反了」鄭若驊外訪開支逾百萬　被炮轟不務正業","createTime":"2018-12-30T15:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T02:35:23.000Z","uid":78457,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"63f27db00cf5aa854fba4c77bf6ea11fb5d81c6d","tid":962130,"uid":78457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"擅改檢控準則捱轟的律政司司長鄭若驊，上任將滿一年，東網翻查鄭上任至今的外訪紀錄，發現她的外訪開支突破一百萬港元，達一百一十七萬七千港元，十二次外訪總日數達到三十九天，即逾一個月不在港，足迹遍布英美日韓。「廿三萬監察」發言人、前立法會議員王國興狠批鄭若驊的立法會出席率低，違法佔中搞手不檢控，但又頻頻外訪，予人不務正業的感覺。有學者更直斥鄭本末倒置，醜聞纒身就外訪逃避傳媒狙擊，應該<span style=\"color: red;\">引咎辭職。</span>"},{"pid":"d99096fb21d04fe2546c8dc4506b8eeffc7521e4","tid":962130,"uid":89683,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"擅改檢控準則捱轟的律政司司長"},{"pid":"4c596e590c46fe4536bb4624120f3bce734634a7","tid":962130,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"告肥佬黎咪一天都光晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6002b89fac0b2a8de136c0139da149b29673756","tid":962130,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c596e590c46fe4536bb4624120f3bce734634a7","tid":962130,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"告肥佬黎咪一天都光晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"原來如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b1c5814ea99355d8b0c33b6f67710c5a5fcaf6","tid":962130,"uid":106482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d99096fb21d04fe2546c8dc4506b8eeffc7521e4","tid":962130,"uid":89683,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"擅改檢控準則捱轟的律政司司長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"擅長"},{"p